*Dan*as se zahvaljujem za dar (Today I thank you for the gift). 
Sutra će biti *dan* odmora (Tomorrow will be a day off).
Uvek ću pamtiti prvi *dan* na poslu (I will always remember my first day at work).
Potrebno je da se za *dan* dogovorimo (It is necessary to agree on a day).
Taj *dan* će biti veoma značajan (That day will be very important).